{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1684-03e_084", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Explications en Vers sur les deux Enigmes de la sillabe Mi]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Extraordinaire du Mercure Galant, quartier de janvier [tome 25], 1684, p. 84-92."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Voicy, Madame, ce que j’ay reçeu d’Explications en Vers sur les Enigmes du mois de Decembre, qui avoient esté faites toutes deux sur la sillabe Mi."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": "I."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[5]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Je voy bien, aimable Caliste,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[6]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Et vous aussi, Berger Fleuriste,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[7]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Que pour m’embarrasser vous estes de concert ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[8]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais cela ne vous sert de guére ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[9]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[9]/text()[1]", "text": "De vostre énigmatique Affaire"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[10]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Tout le secret m’est découvert ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[11]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Et pour vous dire enfin ce qui m’en semble,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[12]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Ainsi que vos deux coeurs n’en forment qu’un ensemble,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[13]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[13]/text()[1]", "text": "De vos deux Enigmes aussy"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[14]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous n’en faites qu’une, & c’est Mi."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[15]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Diereville, du Pontlevesque."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[16]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[17]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[17]/text()[1]", "text": "II."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[18]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[18]/text()[1]", "text": "L’Autre jour la jeune Angélique,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[19]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[19]/text()[1]", "text": "En me voyant triste & rêveur ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[20]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[20]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu’as-tu fait de ta belle humeur,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[21]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[21]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour estre si mélancolique,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[22]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[22]/text()[1]", "text": "Me dit-elle d’un ton railleur ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[23]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[23]/text()[1]", "text": "Ah ! cruelle, c’est ta rigueur,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[24]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[24]/text()[1]", "text": "Luy dis-je, qui fait ma douleur."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[25]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[25]/text()[1]", "text": "Il faut soulager ton martyre,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[26]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[26]/text()[1]", "text": "Dit-elle, faisant un soûrire ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[27]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[27]/text()[1]", "text": "Ecoute-moy chanter un Recit d’Amadis,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[28]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[28]/text()[1]", "text": "Tous les Airs en sont aplaudis ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[29]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[29]/text()[1]", "text": "Je vais te charmer par l’oreille."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[30]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[30]/text()[1]", "text": "Elle chante, & si-tost que son Air fut finy,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[31]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[31]/text()[1]", "text": "La Folette me dit, n’ay-je pas fait merveille ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[32]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[32]/text()[1]", "text": "Je n’ay pas manqué d’un seul Mi."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[33]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[33]/text()[1]", "text": "Il est vray que ta voix enchante,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[34]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[34]/text()[1]", "text": "Luy dis-je, & ta méthode a beaucoup d’agrément."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[35]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[35]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais helas ! que me sert qu’elle soit si charmante,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[36]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[36]/text()[1]", "text": "Si je n’en reçoy pas quelque soulagement ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[37]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[37]/text()[1]", "text": "Le mesme."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[38]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[39]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[39]/text()[1]", "text": "III."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[40]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[40]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous méritez beaucoup, admirable Calliste ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[41]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[41]/text()[1]", "text": "Cependant pouvez-vous donner le nom d’Amy"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[42]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[42]/text()[1]", "text": "Au galant & sage Fleuriste ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[43]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[43]/text()[1]", "text": "Non, vous ne le pouvez, sans la sillabe Mi."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[44]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[44]/text()[1]", "text": "Cyges."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[45]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[46]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[46]/text()[1]", "text": "IV."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[47]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[47]/text()[1]", "text": "Peut-on, divin Courrier, qu’on aime & qu’on estime,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[48]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[48]/text()[1]", "text": "Se bien se ressouvenir que l’on est vostre Amy,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[49]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[49]/text()[1]", "text": "Sans découvrir le Mot de l’une & l’autre Enigme,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[50]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[50]/text()[1]", "text": "Puis qu’on ne peut donner son suffrage qu’à Mi ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[51]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[51]/text()[1]", "text": "Le mesme."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[52]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[53]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[53]/text()[1]", "text": "V."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[54]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[54]/text()[1]", "text": "Quoy ! l’on a quatre pieds, un Plumet sur l’oreille,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[55]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[55]/text()[1]", "text": "Sans estre Fille, ny Garçon,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[56]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[56]/text()[1]", "text": "Et mesme ny Chair, ny Poisson."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[57]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[57]/text()[1]", "text": "Fut-il jamais chose pareille ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[58]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[58]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous nous l’enseignerez, Mercure nostre Amy ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[59]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[59]/text()[1]", "text": "Je croy pourtant que c’est un Mi."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[60]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[60]/text()[1]", "text": "L’Exilée de la Ville-Françoise."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[61]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[62]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[62]/text()[1]", "text": "VI."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[63]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[63]/text()[1]", "text": "Je fais plus de cas des deux Mi"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[64]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[64]/text()[1]", "text": "Que j’ay reçeus, Galant Mercure,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[65]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[65]/text()[1]", "text": "Par vostre derniere voiture,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[66]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[66]/text()[1]", "text": "Que de tout ce qu peut me venir d’un Amy."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[67]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[67]/text()[1]", "text": "Que ce travail me plaist ! Il est de deux Aimables,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[68]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[68]/text()[1]", "text": "Que je veux croire Amans inséparables."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[69]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[69]/text()[1]", "text": "Il n’est rien de plus achevé,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[70]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[70]/text()[1]", "text": "Les plus fâcheux l’ont approuvé."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[71]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[71]/text()[1]", "text": "La Belle Nourriture."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[72]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[73]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[73]/text()[1]", "text": "VII."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[74]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[74]/text()[1]", "text": "Tout jeune que je suis, j’ay l’esprit vif souvent,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[75]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[75]/text()[1]", "text": "Je descens de quelqu’un qui voit courir le vent ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[76]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[76]/text()[1]", "text": "Des Enigmes du mois j’ay déchiffré l’Arabe,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[77]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[77]/text()[1]", "text": "J’y trouve de mon nom l’une & l’autre sillabe ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[78]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[78]/text()[1]", "text": "Et pour ne rien dire à demy,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[79]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[79]/text()[1]", "text": "C’est que l’on m’appelle Mimi."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[80]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[80]/text()[1]", "text": "Mimi-Mi... de la huitiéme Classe de Geneve."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[81]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[82]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[82]/text()[1]", "text": "VIII."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[83]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[83]/text()[1]", "text": "J’estois encor presqu’endormy,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[84]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[84]/text()[1]", "text": "Quand on m’apporta le Mercure,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[85]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[85]/text()[1]", "text": "Des Enigmes pourtant je cherchay la lecture ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[86]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[86]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais quoy, toutes les deux ne contenoient qu’un Mi."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[87]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[87]/text()[1]", "text": "Alcidor, du Havre."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[88]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[89]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[89]/text()[1]", "text": "IX."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[90]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[90]/text()[1]", "text": "Me trompay-je, Mercure, ou bien ay-je raison,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[91]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[91]/text()[1]", "text": "De croire que les deux Enigmes"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[92]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[92]/text()[1]", "text": "Ont une telle liaison,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[93]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[93]/text()[1]", "text": "Que dans l’une on voit l’autre, & que toutes leurs rimes"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[94]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[94]/text()[1]", "text": "Ne cachent à nos yeux que la sillabe Mi ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[95]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[95]/text()[1]", "text": "Je l’ay gagé contre un Amy."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[96]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[96]/text()[1]", "text": "Le mesme."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[97]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[98]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[98]/text()[1]", "text": "X."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[99]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[99]/text()[1]", "text": "Aux Autheurs des deux Enigmes."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[100]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[101]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[101]/text()[1]", "text": "Admirables Bergers, dont les charmans Ouvrages"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[102]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[102]/text()[1]", "text": "Ont autant de raport que de perfections,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[103]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[103]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous faites juger aux plus sages"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[104]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[104]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu’on n’en trouve pas moins dans vos affections ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[105]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[105]/text()[1]", "text": "Car lors que l’on a veu de l’aimable Caliste"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[106]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[106]/text()[1]", "text": "Une Enigme sur la Beauté,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[107]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[107]/text()[1]", "text": "Elle avoit seulement le droit de primauté"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[108]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[108]/text()[1]", "text": "Sur le galant Berger Fleuriste ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[109]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[109]/text()[1]", "text": "Et le Si merveilleux, avec tous ses détours,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[110]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[110]/text()[1]", "text": "Fut-il pas déguisé par le mesme secours ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[111]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[111]/text()[1]", "text": "Ainsi cette union qu’on trouve inséparable,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[112]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[112]/text()[1]", "text": "Nous fait voir en ce mois, d’un stile incompparable,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[113]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[113]/text()[1]", "text": "Que vous, belle Caliste, imitant vostre Amy,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[114]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[114]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous vous estes encor rencontrez sur le Mi."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[115]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[115]/text()[1]", "text": "Le mesme."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[116]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[117]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[117]/text()[1]", "text": "XI."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[118]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[118]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous ne nous étrennez, Mercure, qu’à demy,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[119]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[119]/text()[1]", "text": "Dans ce premier mois de l’Année."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[120]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[120]/text()[1]", "text": "Croyez-vous que je sois satisfaite d’un Mi ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[121]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[121]/text()[1]", "text": "Non, Seigneur, j’espérais estre mieux étrennée."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[122]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[122]/text()[1]", "text": "Sylvin, du Havre."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[123]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[124]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[124]/text()[1]", "text": "XII."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[125]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[125]/text()[1]", "text": "Le chagrin d’avoir veu mon Berger me quitter,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[126]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[126]/text()[1]", "text": "M’avoit fait renoncer, Mercure, à ces Enigmes ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[127]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[127]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais depuis que je voy qu’il revient m’en conter,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[128]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[128]/text()[1]", "text": "Je reprens du plaisir à rêver sur leurs rimes."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[129]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[129]/text()[1]", "text": "Lors que pour un Amant on ressent de l’amour,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[130]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[130]/text()[1]", "text": "Et que son changement chagrine,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[131]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[131]/text()[1]", "text": "A quoy sert de faire la fine ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[132]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[132]/text()[1]", "text": "On est bien-aise du retour,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[133]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[133]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour moy, tant que dure le jour."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[134]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[134]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour en marquer mon allégresse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[135]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[135]/text()[1]", "text": "Apres un rigoureux ennuy,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[136]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[136]/text()[1]", "text": "Je ne fais que chanter sans cesse"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[137]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[137]/text()[1]", "text": "Ut re mi fa, fa sol fa Mi."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[138]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[138]/text()[1]", "text": "Il ne faut pas que l’on me blâme"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[139]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[139]/text()[1]", "text": "De l’aveu que je te fais là,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[140]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[140]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure, car malgré cela,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[141]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[141]/text()[1]", "text": "Je suis toûjours la Belle à l’Anagramme."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[142]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[142]/text()[1]", "text": "Libre d’amour, de la Ruë du Bac."}]}]}